import React from 'react'; import '../styles/About.css'; const About = () => { return (
{/* Minimalist Hero Section */}
About Us

A team of digital innovators helping small businesses succeed

Since 2018, we've been partnering with small businesses to create impactful digital experiences that drive growth and deliver results.

5+ Years Experience
200+ Happy Clients
25+ Team Members
{/* Mission Statement */}

Our Mission

To empower small businesses with enterprise-quality digital solutions at prices they can afford, helping them compete and thrive in the modern marketplace.

{/* Our Story Section */}

Our Story

2018

Where It All Began

Seraune was founded by Alex Morgan and Samantha Chen, who saw that small businesses needed better technology partners. Coming from enterprise tech backgrounds, they wanted to bring that expertise to companies with limited budgets but big ambitions.

2020

Period of Growth

We expanded our team to 15 members and launched our cloud solutions division, offering small businesses the same level of secure infrastructure previously only available to larger corporations.

2023

Today

With a team of 25+ specialists across different disciplines, we've successfully helped over 200 businesses transform their digital presence and operations, always focusing on delivering measurable results.

{/* Values Section */}

Our Core Values

These principles guide every decision we make and every project we undertake

01

Client Partnership

We don't just work for our clients—we work with them. Your success is our success, and we're invested in seeing your business thrive.

02

Quality Without Compromise

We believe small businesses deserve the same quality of work as large corporations. We never cut corners or deliver anything less than our best.

03

Transparent Communication

Clear, honest communication is the foundation of every successful project. We keep you informed and involved every step of the way.

04

Continuous Innovation

Technology evolves rapidly, and so do we. We're constantly learning, exploring, and implementing new tools and approaches to give our clients an edge.

{/* Team Section */}

Meet Our Team

The talented people behind Seraune's success

Leadership

Alex Morgan

Founder & CEO

With 15+ years in tech consulting, Alex founded Seraune to bring enterprise-level solutions to small businesses.

Samantha Chen

Co-Founder & CTO

Former Google engineer with expertise in creating scalable web applications and custom software solutions.

Department Heads

{/* Work Environment */}

Our Workplace

We believe a positive, collaborative environment helps us do our best work. Our San Francisco office is designed to foster creativity, collaboration, and wellbeing.

Collaborative Culture

Cross-functional teams work together to leverage diverse skills and perspectives.

Flexible Working

We value work-life balance and offer flexible schedules to support our team's wellbeing.

Continuous Learning

We invest in our team's growth with ongoing training, conferences, and education opportunities.

{/* Client Testimonial */}
"
Working with Seraune has been transformative for our business. They didn't just build us a website—they created a comprehensive digital strategy that has increased our leads by 70% and given us a competitive edge we didn't have before.

Sarah Johnson

CEO, Bright Interiors
